# Icons – PandaTrack

Use two icon sources depending on the use case:

- **Lucide Icons** (`lucide-react`): General-purpose UI icons (arrows, mail, settings, layout, etc.).
- **Simple Icons** (`simple-icons`): Brand icons only (TikTok, Instagram, GitHub, etc.). See [simple-icons](https://github.com/simple-icons/simple-icons).

When rendering a Simple Icon in JSX, use the icon’s `path` inside an `<svg>` with `viewBox="0 0 24 24"` and `fill="currentColor"` so it matches text color.
